  "texts": [
    "A total of 17 of these prompts contained only parameter values ('data prompts'), with the remaining 16 prompts describing methodology and assumptions ('method prompts').",
    "The final prompt set for the RCC model used 21 data prompts and 16 method prompts.",
    "All final prompts are provided in the Online Resource.The method prompts differed in length depending on the complexity of the methods described.",
    "Figure 5a provides an example of a simple method prompt for the RCC model and the data prompts to which it was linked, and Fig. 5b provides an example of a complex method prompt for the NSCLC model.",
    "For sections of the models that required multi-step methodology, performance was generally improved by explicitly setting out the methodological steps in order."
  ],
